  Function: hr2int
      Desc: Return integer from human-readable number text
          : (b)ytes (k)ilobytes (m)egabytes (g)igabytes (t)erabytes 
          : (p)etabytes
          : Capitalise to use multiples of 1000 (S.I.) instead of 1024.
          : test:
  Synopsis: hr2int integer[bkmgtp] [integer[bkmgtp]]...
   Example: hr2int 34M
          : hr2int 34m
          : hr2int 34000000
       Url: file:///usr/share/okusi/entities/entities.d/sys/hr2int.bash
